h1. Resources

Listing of links, books, and other important reference resources used in the development of the roadmap.

* "Adafruit tutorial on managing multiple tasks at the same time in Arduino":https://learn.adafruit.com/multi-tasking-the-arduino-part-1 - may be helpful for sensor based projects
* "Beagle Bone Black resources":http://inspire.logicsupply.com/ - lots of good material on using BBB in engineering and science applications